        {
            "name": "Description",
            "type": "section",
            "html": "The glyptodon is often hunted for the value of its outer armor, made up of bony plates in turn composed of many smaller, knobby \u201cscales.\u201d The creature is quite capable of defending itself with swipes from its deadly claws, as its ill-tempered nature often urges it to do."
